 [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a four-hour time difference for the 2016 Brazil games, which kicked off at midnight in Britain and had an average of 3.8 million viewers.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5986758194749329, \"rank\": 0.6699767574671915, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999998881322, \"rank\": 1.1185586568910976e-10, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite millions of fans tuning into the Paris opening ceremony, some were left feeling cold the event, with @EmiEleode fuming on X: 'I am sorry but the Paris Olympics #OpeningCeremony is bad.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.674617773732437e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not believe the mess I am watching.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing so far has matched the London 2012 one which was spectacular.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 2.22